00:12:22.882 --> 00:12:23.763
Not the best.

00:12:26.825 --> 00:12:28.987
Now, on to Mococo.

00:12:30.888 --> 00:12:31.468
Mococo!

00:12:32.956 --> 00:12:35.058
As the runt, she gets me a bit more.

00:12:35.198 --> 00:12:36.679
