00:13:11.255 --> 00:13:11.675
Yeah.

00:13:12.636 --> 00:13:13.076
Yeah.

00:13:14.577 --> 00:13:15.738
How do you feel about it?

00:13:17.519 --> 00:13:18.219
Be honest.

00:13:18.779 --> 00:13:19.260
Go on.

00:13:21.841 --> 00:13:22.362
Pet?

00:13:23.102 --> 00:13:24.363
You can't pet me.

00:13:24.763 --> 00:13:25.844
I'm the Great Perroccino.

00:13:30.271 --> 00:13:30.811
Same.

00:13:31.732 --> 00:13:32.252
Got me.

00:13:32.913 --> 00:13:37.856
Maybe the Ruffians, maybe you and I are a bit closer than you thought, huh?

00:13:40.997 --> 00:13:50.063
But you know, Fuwawa and Mococo, together, I think they have the potential to be pretty strong.

00:13:51.664 --> 00:13:56.086
