00:14:48.174 --> 00:14:49.955
I'm just here to train them, okay?

00:14:50.775 --> 00:14:51.796
They gotta be tough.

00:14:53.746 --> 00:14:55.907
Oh, and that's right.

00:14:56.908 --> 00:14:57.869
I heard some things.

00:15:00.350 --> 00:15:04.633
